# 止蝕

(pos:名詞)
<explanation>
yue:指做某件嘢可以補償之前嘅損失，令到收支平衡（量詞：個）
eng:break-even point or a situation where losses are offset by gains

<eg>
yue:我今次嘅生意止蝕咗。 (ngo5 ging4 ci3 zoi3 sing1 bei1 ji6 zing3 zit6 zit6 zit6 yih6 zit6.)
eng:I managed to break even with my business this time.

yue:佢今次嘅投資止蝕咗。 (keoi5 ging4 ci3 zoi3 tou1 zi1 zing3 zit6 zit6 zit6 yih6 zit6.)
eng:His investment this time broke even. 

yue:我搵到份新工止蝲咗。 (ngo5 waan5 dou6 faan3 sing1 gung1 zing3 zit6 zit6 zit6 yih6 zit6.)
eng:I found a new job that covers my expenses and breaks even. 

(注意：「止蝕」通常用嚟形容收支平衡，但亦可以用嚟形容某件嘢可以補償之前嘅損失。) 

